{
  "starter_key": "amazon_ad_analysis_v1",
  "starter_version": 5,
  "name": "Amazon 广告数据深度分析",
  "description": "文件输入 + Agent 初判 + 并行复核 + 结果校验，自动输出可执行投放方案。",
  "category": "亚马逊运营",
  "workflow_type": "graph",
  "tags": [
    "amazon",
    "ads",
    "analysis",
    "validation",
    "parallel",
    "multi-agent"
  ],
  "config": {
    "schemaVersion": 2,
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "start-ad",
        "type": "start",
        "position": {
          "x": 80,
          "y": 220
        },
        "data": {
          "type": "start",
          "label": "输入广告数据",
          "description": "在开始节点填写本轮分析目标",
          "icon": "🚀",
          "iconColor": "bg-blue-500"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "input-file-ad",
        "type": "input_file",
        "position": {
          "x": 300,
          "y": 220
        },
        "data": {
          "type": "input_file",
          "label": "广告报表文件",
          "description": "上传 SP/SB/SD 搜索词报表（Excel/CSV）",
          "icon": "📎",
          "iconColor": "bg-cyan-500",
          "startFileUrl": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "input-text-ad",
        "type": "input_text",
        "position": {
          "x": 540,
          "y": 220
        },
        "data": {
          "type": "input_text",
          "label": "分析目标",
          "description": "例如：目标 ACoS 30%，先控亏再放量",
          "icon": "📝",
          "iconColor": "bg-emerald-500",
          "startTask": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "agent-ad-optimize",
        "type": "agent",
        "position": {
          "x": 780,
          "y": 220
        },
        "data": {
          "type": "agent",
          "label": "广告优化初判",
          "description": "解析广告报表并输出否定词/加投词初稿",
          "icon": "🧩",
          "iconColor": "bg-indigo-500",
          "agentName": "亚马逊广告分析师",
          "agentTaskType": "data-analysis",
          "agentFileUrl": "{{input-file-ad.output.fileUrl}}",
          "inputMapping": "广告目标：{{input-text-ad.output.text}}\\n报表文件：{{input-file-ad.output.fileUrl}}\\n\\n请先完成广告优化初判：\\n1. 否定词候选\\n2. 加投词候选\\n3. 预算与竞价初始建议。",
          "instructions": "请先自动识别表头并做字段映射（支持中英文/别名字段），至少识别：search term、impressions、clicks、spend、orders、sales。\\n如存在缺失字段，明确标记并给出降级分析策略。\\n输出结构化初判：negativeKeywords、scaleUpKeywords、budgetActions、riskNotes；每项都给出触发依据（点击、花费、ACoS、CVR等）。"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "parallel-ad-review",
        "type": "parallel",
        "position": {
          "x": 1020,
          "y": 220
        },
        "data": {
          "type": "parallel",
          "label": "并行复核",
          "description": "并行评估数据质量、广告动作与预算策略",
          "icon": "⚡",
          "iconColor": "bg-yellow-500",
          "joinMode": "wait_all"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "agent-data-overview",
        "type": "agent",
        "position": {
          "x": 1260,
          "y": 80
        },
        "data": {
          "type": "agent",
          "label": "数据质量复核",
          "description": "核对字段映射、口径和异常值风险",
          "icon": "📈",
          "iconColor": "bg-cyan-500",
          "agentName": "数据报表分析师",
          "inputMapping": "广告目标：{{input-text-ad.output.text}}\\n报表文件：{{input-file-ad.output.fileUrl}}\\n优化初判：{{agent-ad-optimize.output.text}}",
          "instructions": "请只做“数据可靠性复核”：\n1. 字段映射是否正确（搜索词、花费、销售、订单）\n2. 统计口径是否一致（总量/均值/占比）\n3. 标注异常与样本不足风险\n4. 输出可信度评分（0-100）和风险清单\n5. 若换任意同类型 Excel，说明该流程如何自动适配（字段别名、空值、货币/百分比格式差异）"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "agent-ad-deep",
        "type": "agent",
        "position": {
          "x": 1260,
          "y": 220
        },
        "data": {
          "type": "agent",
          "label": "广告深度分析",
          "description": "按 PPC 视角审阅否定词与加投词",
          "icon": "📊",
          "iconColor": "bg-blue-500",
          "agentName": "亚马逊广告分析师",
          "inputMapping": "广告目标：{{input-text-ad.output.text}}\\n优化初判：{{agent-ad-optimize.output.text}}",
          "instructions": "请只做“广告动作复核”：\n1. 否定词候选按 P0/P1 分级（是否立即执行）\n2. 加投词候选按预期收益排序\n3. 给出竞价/预算调整建议（加价/降价/暂停）\n4. 输出执行前置条件和风险提示"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "agent-budget-review",
        "type": "agent",
        "position": {
          "x": 1260,
          "y": 360
        },
        "data": {
          "type": "agent",
          "label": "预算策略复核",
          "description": "从经营目标角度评估投入与回报平衡",
          "icon": "🧮",
          "iconColor": "bg-violet-500",
          "agentName": "运营策略顾问",
          "inputMapping": "广告目标：{{input-text-ad.output.text}}\\n优化初判：{{agent-ad-optimize.output.text}}",
          "instructions": "请只做“预算复核”：\n1. 按目标 ACoS 评估预算上/下调空间\n2. 标注可放量词与应降本词\n3. 给出 7 天预算节奏建议\n4. 输出风险阈值（何时暂停/回滚）"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "merge-ad-review",
        "type": "merge",
        "position": {
          "x": 1500,
          "y": 220
        },
        "data": {
          "type": "merge",
          "label": "复核汇总",
          "description": "汇总多视角复核结果",
          "icon": "🔗",
          "iconColor": "bg-gray-500",
          "mergeStrategy": "append"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "agent-ad-validation",
        "type": "agent",
        "position": {
          "x": 1740,
          "y": 220
        },
        "data": {
          "type": "agent",
          "label": "一致性校验",
          "description": "校验矛盾项并给出最终可信结论",
          "icon": "✅",
          "iconColor": "bg-emerald-500",
          "agentName": "数据报表分析师",
          "inputMapping": "并行复核汇总：{{merge-ad-review.output.text}}",
          "instructions": "请对上游三个复核结果做一致性校验：\n1. 找出结论冲突点并解释原因\n2. 保留有数据支撑的建议，剔除弱证据建议\n3. 输出“通过/有条件通过/不通过”结论\n4. 给出最终执行前检查清单"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "agent-strategy",
        "type": "agent",
        "position": {
          "x": 1980,
          "y": 220
        },
        "data": {
          "type": "agent",
          "label": "执行方案",
          "description": "输出可直接落地的投放行动计划",
          "icon": "🧠",
          "iconColor": "bg-indigo-500",
          "agentName": "运营策略顾问",
          "inputMapping": "已校验结论：{{agent-ad-validation.output.text}}",
          "instructions": "请基于“已校验结论”输出最终执行方案：\n1. 未来 7 天行动清单（P0/P1/P2）\n2. 否定词执行顺序（含阈值）\n3. 加投词预算/竞价调整表\n4. 预期指标变化区间（ACoS/订单/花费）\n5. 复盘指标与回滚条件"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "end-ad",
        "type": "end",
        "position": {
          "x": 2220,
          "y": 220
        },
        "data": {
          "type": "end",
          "label": "分析报告",
          "description": "输出完整的广告分析报告",
          "icon": "🏁",
          "iconColor": "bg-green-500"
        }
      }
    ],
    "edges": [
      {
        "id": "e-ad-1",
        "source": "start-ad",
        "target": "input-file-ad"
      },
      {
        "id": "e-ad-2",
        "source": "input-file-ad",
        "target": "input-text-ad"
      },
      {
        "id": "e-ad-3",
        "source": "input-text-ad",
        "target": "agent-ad-optimize"
      },
      {
        "id": "e-ad-4",
        "source": "agent-ad-optimize",
        "target": "parallel-ad-review"
      },
      {
        "id": "e-ad-5",
        "source": "parallel-ad-review",
        "target": "agent-data-overview"
      },
      {
        "id": "e-ad-6",
        "source": "parallel-ad-review",
        "target": "agent-ad-deep"
      },
      {
        "id": "e-ad-7",
        "source": "parallel-ad-review",
        "target": "agent-budget-review"
      },
      {
        "id": "e-ad-8",
        "source": "agent-data-overview",
        "target": "merge-ad-review"
      },
      {
        "id": "e-ad-9",
        "source": "agent-ad-deep",
        "target": "merge-ad-review"
      },
      {
        "id": "e-ad-10",
        "source": "agent-budget-review",
        "target": "merge-ad-review"
      },
      {
        "id": "e-ad-11",
        "source": "merge-ad-review",
        "target": "agent-ad-validation"
      },
      {
        "id": "e-ad-12",
        "source": "agent-ad-validation",
        "target": "agent-strategy"
      },
      {
        "id": "e-ad-13",
        "source": "agent-strategy",
        "target": "end-ad"
      }
    ]
  }
}
